### ========================================================
### 1. AUTH
### ========================================================

### Registrar un nuevo usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Usuario Test",
  "email": "usuario@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login (usuario normal)
# @name loginUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "usuario@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login (admin)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@inmobiliaria.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

