### ========================================================
### 2. USERS (solo admin)
### ========================================================

### Obtener todos los usuarios (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Eliminar un usuario (admin) - cambiar el ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ========================================================
### 3. PROPIEDADES
### ========================================================

### Crear propiedad con imágenes en base64 (simulado, usa strings cortos de ejemplo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Casa en la playa",
  "description": "Hermosa casa frente al mar",
  "price": 250000,
  "province": "Málaga",
  "city": "Marbella",
  "street": "Calle del Mar 12",
  "bedrooms": 4,
  "bathrooms": 2,
  "area": 180,
  "propertytype": "casa",
  "occupied": false,
  "reo": false,
  "lat": 36.5082,
  "lng": -4.8833,
  "images": ["data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=="]
}

### Crear propiedad con FormData (archivos) - no se puede probar fácilmente en .rest, pero se puede con Postman
### En .rest no soporta multipart, así que se omite. Para probar multer usa Postman o frontend.

### Obtener todas las propiedades (con paginación y filtros)
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?page=1&limit=5&province=Málaga

### Obtener propiedad por ID (cambiar el ID por uno real)
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties/1

### Actualizar propiedad (PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/properties/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Casa en la playa (actualizada)",
  "price": 260000,
  "bedrooms": 5
}

### Eliminar propiedad (cambiar ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/properties/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ========================================================
### 4. FAVORITOS
### ========================================================

### Añadir propiedad a favoritos (cambiar ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Obtener favoritos del usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Eliminar de favoritos (cambiar ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/favorites/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

